function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ActorKill(ID_BLOCKER)

	
	------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drorp occurs
		-- idFirstTimeRewardLocation is set/created on "Actor Killed)
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Duriel", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Duriel")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convDurielKill, idActorKiller)
end

function Start()

	CurrentDurielPlayer = Hydra.ActorGetClosestPlayer(markerDurielSpawn_Location)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(CurrentDurielPlayer) == true then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convDurielSpawn, CurrentDurielPlayer)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	local POWER_DEBRIS = Hydra.ReferencePower("QST_Kehj_Caldeum_Debris")
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(markerDurielDebris_04A, POWER_DEBRIS)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(markerDurielDebris_04B, POWER_DEBRIS)
	local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActors()
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		if (Hydra.ActorDistanceBetweenActors(idActor, idPlayer) < 15) then
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_CAMERA_SHAKE_POWER, "Shake_Lrg", idPlayer)
			Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idPlayer, soundShakeLrg)
		end
	end
end
